Azure VM creation
# ☁️ Azure VM Setup & Jenkins Installation Guide

This guide walks you through the steps to:

1. ✅ Create a Virtual Machine (VM) on Microsoft Azure
2. 🛠️ Install and Configure Jenkins on the Azure VM

---

