- [Steps Overview](#steps-overview)
- [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
- [VM Creation Steps](#vm-creation-steps)
- [Jenkins Installation Steps](#jenkins-installation-steps)
- [Screenshots & Word Doc](#screenshots--word-doc)
